+@conformance
+Feature: Shipshape methodology conformance
+
+  @captain
+  Scenario: Watchbill shape conforms when absent
+    Given no watchbill.json exists at the project root
+    When the watchbill shape check runs
+    Then the check passes with an absent watchbill
+
+  @captain
+  Scenario: No perturbation token stands in implementation
+    Given the implementation directories contain no live perturbation
+    When the perturbation quiescence check scans "src"
+    Then no line matches the literal token "PERTURBATION"
